  m_text: 'The ranged goblin is the pinnacle of goblin evolution, as it knows that
    getting too close can be dangerous.

    Therefore it will keep it''s distance
    while launching snowballs towards you which can damage on impact.

    However,
    if the snowball lands on the ice rink, it will leave a gaping hole behind!'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
