  m_text: 'While ice skating arounf the rink, you can build up your attack combo
    so when the time comes where you face off with a goblin, you''ll be able to attack.

    Pressing
    the SPACE key will make you do a twirl above the ice, this will increase your
    current attack combo by 1 (minimum of 0, maximum of 5).


    To signal how much
    attack combo you currently have, a blue music note will appear next to your character
    alongside a musical cue (1-4 : C-F Notes, 5 : C major).'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
